message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8

𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8

In partnership with:
FEU ITHM Music Makers
FEU Sexuality and Gender Alliance

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms!

message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:

message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8

In partnership with:
FEU ITHM Music Makers
FEU Sexuality and Gender Alliance 
TAMang Boto

Caption by: Ysha Patapat
Pubmat by: Layza Tolomia

#WTD2025

message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

A small favor lang po. We are currently conducting a nursing research and are looking for newly graduated nurses who are currently working in hospitals within Metro Manila. 

I’m asking for your help in answering this survey for our thesis

If you meet the following criteria, we would sincerely appreciate your participation:

✅ Registered Nurse in the Philippines

✅ Currently residing in Metro Manila

✅ Employed in a hospital for not more than 2 years after graduation

Your response will greatly help us in completing our thesis.
